- Add event-system.js: 11 wave modifiers, 10 surprise events, scaling director
- Add boss-archetypes.js: 6 unique boss archetypes with special behaviors
- Extend invader-system.js: 7 new enemy types (zigzag, splitter, healer, sniper,
  kamikaze, cloaked, golden) + mutation system
- Extend upgrade-system.js: rarity system, 10 new upgrades (piercing, chain
  lightning, explosive rounds, shield regen, auto bomb, slow dodge, magnet
  powerups, boss damage, revive, double drone), risk/reward mechanics
- Extend render-system.js: draw all new enemy types, boss archetypes, wave
  modifier overlays, event banners, mutation flash, asteroid/laser/EMP/panic
  effects, risk/reward selection screen with rarity borders
- Extend bootstrap.js: wire all new systems into game loop — new state vars,
  updated startWave/update/completeWave/onKeyDown/draw/resetGame, scaling
  director ticking, surprise event triggering, piercing/chain/explosive bullet
  mechanics, revive intercept, slow dodge double-tap, shield regen, EMP,
  panic mode, boss damage boost, wave score multiplier

